data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER/BRING ALL OFFERS. Seller will pay for $600.00 Home Warranty. This property has many options, it can stay a single family residence with its new carpet and paint on the main floor with 2 beds 1 bath and a separate basement entrance with a non conforming bed/bath w/potential to finish for in law, guest suite or studio/office or you can work with The Greater SL Municipal Service District and look at their new vision for Magna Main Street. A new Neighborhood Mixed Use District or a Corridor Mixed Use District are some of the options that SL County has put in place for this area. The RDA has also been assisting in the redevelopment of the area. As you will notice there are many changes happening along Magna Main St. A new Police Station, Fire Station and many new buildings and plans are underway to make this area walkable and inviting. The County has expressed that they would like to see LIVE/WORK, RETAIL or  something similar on this corner but are open to ideas to support the health and vitality of the neighborhood. Some rooms are virtually staged. Please see MLS#1894305
